<BaseLayout
  title="Customer Reviews | 5-Star Rated Roofer | Happy Roof"
  description="Read real Google reviews from Happy Roof customers in Tampa Bay. 5.0-star rating. See what homeowners say about our roofing work, warranties, and service."
  canonical="https://happyroof.com/reviews"
  ogTitle="Customer Reviews | Happy Roof Tampa Bay"
